    {
      "chinese": "以前的比賽項目和現代運動不同。日本時代增加國際運動比賽，現代更發展出新項目，跟以前的賽跑不一樣了，也有拳擊、游泳、射箭、野球（棒球）等球類及正式項目。",
      "ab": "Ku nadruma, ku nimakalrualrumalane sidrumane kaikaungudukadhane; sakelanga kay Dripungu mailuku ku maelane ku makalrualrualrumale ki yakaumasane, kikaynga laaruedhale kay drumane, kikay makaela ki alailadhane si kakathane, kikay wabukusingi, walanguy walredeedepe, wapapana, wayakiw. Kikaynga langiamalrialri si lakaungudukadhane.",
